<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Office of Personnel Management may prescribe regulations necessary for the administration of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb89a4e18-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/554">Pub. L. 89–554</ref>, <date date="1966-09-06">Sept. 6, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/521">80 Stat. 521</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/95/454/tIX/s906/a/2">Pub. L. 95–454, title IX, § 906(a)(2)</ref>, <date date="1978-10-13">Oct. 13, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/1224">92 Stat. 1224</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
